3. e5 Ng8
{ This retreat does not make so much sense. Black is far from being able to justify the move e5 as an overextension and, after the central break, White has a lot of development and space advantage. White has a lot of development and space advantage. }
4. d4 cxd4 5. Qxd4 Nc6 6. Qf4
{ We have moved our Queen, so it makes sense to bring it to a better square instead of going back. We will see it is a very safe and active square! }
