{ Same idea than in other positions, we will push our pawn to a5 and then we will prepare the c5 break. }
13... a5
{ This kind of move does not work because we will develop all our pieces harmoniously. }
14. Bb5+ Nbd7 15. Ra3
{ The Rook here will have an excellent scope through the third rank for our attacking chances. }
