{ We will go into all the secondary lines after @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pp1ppppp/8/2p5/4P3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQKB1R b KQkq - 1 2@@EndFEN@@  2...d6  . }
4... Nf6 5. Nc3 e5 6. Bb5+ Nbd7
{ This line has gained some followers lately, Harikrishna is one of their supporters from this year. }
7. Nf5 { This is the idea behind our check. Our Knight is safe on f5. } 7... a6
8. Be2
{ Unknown line but it is very good. Our idea is to keep our pair of Bishops and bring the Knight to e3 and our Bishop to f3 as soon as possible to get a strong control over the whole position. }
8... Nb6 9. Ne3 { We will get to the usual Najdorf position. } 9... Be6 10. Bf3
{ We have won the fight to cover the d5-square. } 10... Be7 11. b3 Rc8 12. Bb2
{ This is the ideal setup for White, we have everything under control and the b6-Knight is standing there without any useful moves. }
*

