{ Usually this is not an ideal square for the Knight in these structures. } 4.
d4 cxd4 5. Nxd4 Nf6 6. Nc3 e5 7. Nf5 d5
{ An interesting attempt to unbalance the position.   7...d6  8.Ne3 } 8. cxd5
Bxf5 9. exf5 Nd4 10. Bd3 { Defense and development. } 10... Nxd5
{ The most common, but inaccurate, as we are going to see. } 11. O-O
