Ne4 { Bringing our Knight to the center and attacking their d6-Bishop. } 14...
Bf5 15. Nxd6+ Qxd6 16. Bxf5 Nxf5 17. Qg4
{ Our pieces are really active – we also control the file and have a strong pawn on d5. }
