{ This check is really important to remember. We want to regroup all our pieces. }
16... Bd7 17. Qb4 { We step out but we attack another weakness now. } 17... Nf6
18. Bxc4
{ We will trade this pawn for the e-pawn because we want to have a majority on the Queenside! }
