{ Sacrificing a pawn in exchange for counterplay   11...Qb4  12.Bb3⩲  we can continue our development with Bf4 and kick the Black Queen away from its active position with a3 }
12. Qxe7 Ba6 13. Bxa6 Qxa6 14. Qe2
{ Getting back to safety with tempo since Black doesn't want to trade Queens. We have an extra pawn for no compensation }
