12. Qa4 O-O { If  12...Bd7  13.Bxf5  d6 drops. } 13. Qa3
{ Black doesn’t have a good defense for this pawn. } 13... Re8 14. Bxf5 Bxf5
15. Nxd6 Bf8 16. c5 Bxd6 17. cxd6
{ The dark-square weaknesses and our extra pawn offer us a very comfortable edge. }
