16... Be7 17. c5 Rb8 18. Qa6 Ra8 19. Qc4 Ra4 20. Qc2 dxc5 21. d6 Bxd6 22. Bc4
{ Black can barely move and we are threatening Rxh7 or just resuming our development. }
