{ Hoping to breakthrough on the queenside. } 15... Nh7 16. b4 b6 17. Nb3 g6 18.
Qd2 Nhf6 19. f3 Kh7 20. a4 { Now a5 is under control, and it comes next move. }
20... Bxd5 21. cxd5 { 1-0 Santos Ruiz,M-De Lucas Bello, F, Benasque 2021 } *

