{ We attack a5 and prepare Nd4, taking advantage of the newly created weakness on e6. }
18... Bh4 { 18...Bf6  19.Qxa5 } 19. g3 Bg5 20. Bg1
{ We keep the bishop pair and we continue with Nd4. } *

