8... Be6
{ 8...Be7  9.g4  h5  10.gxh5   @@StartFEN@@r1bqk2r/1p2bppp/p1np1n2/4p3/4P3/1NN1B3/PPP1BPPP/R2QK2R w KQkq - 2 9@@EndFEN@@  9.O-O  O-O  10.f3  is possible as well, with a slight advantage, but, as always, I prefer to recommend less-known lines. }
